    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SimpleSelectOneMenu

    public abstract class SimpleSelectOneMenuBase
extends javax.faces.component.UISelectOne
implements ISimpleSelectOneMenu, IceClientBehaviorHolder
    A simple selection component that uses the browser's native "select" element and integrates with the ACE environment, supporting Themeroller, ARIA, label positioning, and ace:ajax.

    For more information, see the SimpleSelectOneMenu Wiki Documentation.
